Name: The Sails that Display Endeavor
AttributesDescription:
Casting Resonance Liberation Amplifies Resonance Skill DMG of the active Resonator by 90% for 15s.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: Time was too short—he only managed to save a single possession before plunging into the sea. Even as his lungs emptied of air, his grin widened. "Surely, I'm the greatest merchant in the world! Trading my life for my family's future—a bargain like no other!"
